721739f.text:
Morton Street, north side, from Washington to Greenwich Streets, showing the old houses where the Bellas, Hess Building and the 636 Hudson Street loft building will rise. No. 6l7 Washington Street, at the corner, is of brick, but the others are frame.
About 1908.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
